title: Chris Distefano

description:
Stand-Up Comedy King Chris Distefano stops by Good For You to chat cancel culture, jealous lovers, the mafia, and being a dad. We play comedian heads up and burn some bridges. Benton checks in via FaceTime hopped up on pills post op.
